oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Receipt from the Headquarters Department Tennessee and Georgia of the G.A.R.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This receipt from the Headquarters Department of Tennessee and Georgia, Grand Army of the Republic was issued at Knoxville, Tenn. It acknowledges receipt of two quartermaster reports from H.P. Gold in 1887 for the amount of $4.50.
